  }, "v1"), mdx("p", null, "\xCA-x\xEA-chia \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c hai m\u01B0\u01A1i l\u0103m tu\u1ED5i khi l\xEAn ng\xF4i vua v\xE0 tr\u1ECB v\xEC hai m\u01B0\u01A1i ch\xEDn n\u0103m t\u1EA1i Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem. M\u1EB9 \xF4ng t\xEAn A-bi-gia, con g\xE1i c\u1EE7a Xa-cha-ri. "), mdx("h6", {
